OL,3,C'What is your red line?': Iranian
OL,4,Cprofessor urges action over protest
OL,5,Cdeaths
OL,7,FBy ITV News Journalist Maral Shafafy
OL,9,FProfessor Sharifi-Zarchi is one of
OL,10,FIran's most high-profile academics,
OL,11,Fteaching bioinformatics and artificial
OL,12,Fintelligence at Tehran's prestigious
OL,13,FSharif University of Technology, often
OL,14,Fdubbed Iran's answer to MIT.
OL,16,FFor the past two weeks, he has been
OL,17,Fliving in exile, knowing that if he
OL,18,Freturns to Iran, he faces almost
OL,19,Fcertain arrest.
