OL,7,FWith more than 150,000 followers on X,
OL,8,Fthe professor says he will remain
OL,9,Fabroad, not out of fear of
OL,10,Fimprisonment, but out of a sense of
OL,11,Fduty to give voice to Iranians living
OL,12,Funder a continuing internet blackout.
OL,14,F"I didn't want to be only a
OL,15,Fhashtag`'Free Ali,'" he tells ITV News
OL,16,Ffrom an undisclosed location. "I
OL,17,Fdecided to be okay, be here and be a
OL,18,Fvoice of a nation that is under
OL,19,Fblackout"
