OL,7,FHe is facing arrest because of his
OL,8,Foutspoken criticism of the regime's
OL,9,Fbrutal crackdown on anti-government
OL,10,Fprotesters.
OL,12,FProtests erupted across 71 cities in
OL,13,FIran in late December. Although they
OL,14,Finitially centred on currency
OL,15,Fdevaluation and economic hardship,
OL,16,Fthey quickly evolved into calls for
OL,17,Fregime change and broader demands for
OL,18,Fdemocracy.
