OL,7,FThe US-based Human Rights Activists
OL,8,FNews Agency (HRANA) says it has
OL,9,Fverified 4,902 deaths since the unrest
OL,10,Fbegan and is reviewing a further 9,387
OL,11,Fsuspected fatalities.
OL,13,FProfessor Sharifi-Zarchi was in Iran
OL,14,Fat the start of the protests and says
OL,15,Fthey began peacefully. However,
OL,16,Ftensions escalated after he left the
OL,17,Fcountry to attend a training camp for
OL,18,Fgold medallists of the International
OL,19,FOlympiad in Informatics in China.
