OL,7,FWhile there, he learned of the violent
OL,8,Fcrackdown unfolding at home and felt
OL,9,Fcompelled to speak out. He posted on
OL,10,FX: "Ali Khamenei is not my leader,"
OL,11,Freferring to Iran's Supreme Leader,
OL,12,Fthe 86-year-old cleric who has ruled
OL,13,Fsince 1989.
OL,15,F"Those tweets had really big
OL,16,Fconsequences," he says. "I knew I was
OL,17,Fputting my hand into the fire."
