OL,7,FHe adds, "Almost immediately, high-
OL,8,Franking security officials began
OL,9,Fpublicly threatening me," noting,
OL,10,F"That's when I realised I couldn't
OL,11,Freturn home."
OL,13,F"The majority of my friends that have
OL,14,Fbeen able to connect from Iran are
OL,15,Fwaiting for international action,"
OL,16,FProfessor Sharifi Zarchi told ITV News
OL,18,FSoon afterwards, he received a message
OL,19,Ffrom Iran's court system confirming
OL,20,Fhis fears that he would be arrested.
