OL,7,FHe says he could face "several years
OL,8,Fin prison" or, depending on the judge,
OL,9,Fan even harsher sentence.
OL,11,FThis is not the first time he has
OL,12,Ffallen foul of the authorities. During
OL,13,Fthe 2022 protests following the death
OL,14,Fof Mahsa Amini, he was summoned by the
OL,15,Fintelligence agency of Iran,
OL,16,Fquestioned, and suspended from his
OL,17,Fteaching post after publicly
OL,18,Fsupporting student demonstrators.
