OL,7,F"They had a thick book with every
OL,8,Fsingle one of my tweets," he recalls.
OL,9,F"Some were highlighted in green, some
OL,10,Fin pink. They asked me, 'What is the
OL,11,Fpurpose of this? What is the purpose
OL,12,Fof that?' And I answered all of those."
OL,14,FThis time, he says, the repression has
OL,15,Fbeen even more severe, with deep
OL,16,Fpersonal consequences.
