OL,7,FAmong those killed in the protests was
OL,8,Fhis close friend, Parsa Saffar, a
OL,9,Fmedical student at Mashhad University
OL,10,Fof Medical Sciences. He was shot dead
OL,11,Fduring demonstrations in Mashhad.
OL,13,F"He was a brave student, a brilliant
OL,14,Fstudent," Sharifi-Zarchi says. He
OL,15,Frecalls the last time they met, when
OL,16,FSaffar welcomed him warmly at the
OL,17,Fairport at the start of a visit to
OL,18,FMashad.
OL,20,F"That's the last image I have of him.
OL,21,FI really hope he rests in peace."
