OL,7,F"Do you know what that means for a
OL,8,Fteenager? They have seen a lot of
OL,9,Fblood in front of them. Their dearest
OL,10,Fpeople, friends, family members being
OL,11,Fkilled, being murdered."
OL,13,FHis message to the international
OL,14,Fcommunity is that Iranians are still
OL,15,Fwaiting for meaningful support.
OL,17,F"The majority of my friends who have
OL,18,Fbeen able to connect from Iran are
OL,19,Freally waiting for international
OL,20,Faction," he says.
