OL,7,FHe tells ITV News that messaging
OL,8,Fplatforms are still under government
OL,9,Fcontrol, adding "people are really
OL,10,Fwaiting for more of a relaxed
OL,11,Fsituation with the internet, so that
OL,12,Fpeople could use other communication
OL,13,Fmedia like Telegram, WhatsApp...in
OL,14,Forder to provide more information."
OL,16,FDespite the risks he faces, Sharifi-
OL,17,FZarchi says his greatest hope is
OL,18,Fsimply to return to teaching and to a
OL,19,Fnormal life. He longs to go back to
OL,20,Fhis classroom and see his students
OL,21,Ffree from fear and economic pressure.
